<div class="container">
  <div class="wine-container">
    <div class="wine-photo">
      <%= image_tag 'wineclub.png', width:'100%' %>
    </div>
    <div class="wine-text">
      <div class="wine-header">
        <p>
          We are all about sharing our finds with you.<br> Let us do the wine picking and surprise you with hand-selected bottles that reflect Art Du Vin’s philosophy of <span>quality</span>, <span>sustainability</span> and <span>taste.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="wine-details">
        <p>All Art Du Vin Wine Club Members receive 10% off with each visit in addition to pick-up party perks!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="wine-button">
        <h3><span>Join our wine club !</span></h3>
        <p>Stop by our <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir//art+du+vin+long+beach/data=!4m6!4m5!1m1!4e2!1m2!1m1!1s0x80dd310efbc78f77:0x2b7c531a1bcf3024?sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjf-qTh1876AhXWgf0HHRvfA4EQ9Rd6BAhsEAU">location</a> to sign up for our wine club. <br>Online sign up coming soon.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="line">
    <%= image_tag 'line.png', width:'100%'; %>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-header">
    <p>FAQ</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-section">
    <div class="faq-questions">
      <div class="faq-title">
        <p class='title-one'><span>What kind of memberships do you offer?</span></p>
        <p class='line'></p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-response">
    <p><b>- Cherry Membership:</b> 2 Red Bottles Monthly ($55)<br>
    - <b>Junipero Membership:</b> 2 White/Rose/Orange Bottles Monthly ($55)<br>
    - <b>4th Street Membership:</b> 2 Red Bottles/1 Sparkling Bottle/1 White Bottle ($100)<br>
    </p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-title">
        <p class='title-one'><span>When will I be charged and how do I get my wine?</span></p>
        <p class='line'></p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-response">
        <p>Our pick-up parties will be happening on the second or third Wednesday of each month. You will be charged the day prior to the party. Each month you will receive an email with an exact date for the pick-up party.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-title">
        <p class='title-two'><span>What if I’m traveling and can’t pick up the wines for weeks?</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-response">
        <p>We’ve got you. We can keep your wines until the end of the month.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-title">
        <p><span>What if I want to cancel?</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-response">
        <p>No problem! You can cancel any time before the 15th of the month to opt out of the next shipment. When you miss us, sign up again any time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-title">
        <p><span>Will you ship my wine?</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-questions">
        <p>Sorry, we are not yet ready for this step, but we are working on this option for the future.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-photo">
      <%= image_tag 'cal.png', width:'100%;', alt:'calendar' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
